CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1772802691
OL,3,CThree men arrested in London and Wales
OL,4,Con suspicion of spying for China
OL,6,FThree men have been arrested on
OL,7,Fsuspicion of spying for China and
OL,8,F"targeting UK democracy".
OL,10,FThe Metropolitan Police said the
OL,11,Fsuspects ` aged 39, 43 and 68 ` were
OL,12,Farrested by counter-terrorism officers
OL,13,Fin London and Wales after being
OL,14,Faccused of assisting a foreign
OL,15,Fintelligence service.
OL,17,FAll three men remain in custody and
OL,18,Fsearches have been carried out at the
OL,19,Faddresses where they were arrested,
OL,20,Fthe force added.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@XO]
