PN,40702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1772802691
OL,3,CThree men arrested in London and Wales
OL,4,Con suspicion of spying for China
OL,6,FChinese officials in the UK and
OL,7,FBeijing have been given a dressing
OL,8,Fdown, a minister told MPs.
OL,10,FUpdating the Commons, security
OL,11,Fminister Dan Jarvis said there will be
OL,12,F"severe consequences" if it is proven
OL,13,Fthat China attempted to interfere with
OL,14,FUK sovereign affairs.
OL,16,FMr Jarvis said the investigation
OL,17,F"relates to China" and "foreign
OL,18,Finterference targeting UK democracy".
OL,26,@tD@AOUtD@UO]yD@AOUyD@RO]yD@XOUzD@dO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/7
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1772802691
OL,3,CThree men arrested in London and Wales
OL,4,Con suspicion of spying for China
OL,6,FHe told MPs: "Let me be clear, if
OL,7,Fthere is proven evidence of attempts
OL,8,Fby China to interfere with UK
OL,9,Fsovereign affairs, we will impose
OL,10,Fsevere consequences and hold all
OL,11,Factors involved to account.
OL,13,F"The Government is taking robust
OL,14,Faction to ensure the UK's democratic
OL,15,Finstitutions and processes are a hard
OL,16,Ftarget for this activity.
OL,26,@nD@NOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/7
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1772802691
OL,3,CThree men arrested in London and Wales
OL,4,Con suspicion of spying for China
OL,6,F"The National Security Act provides
OL,7,Four intelligence agencies and law
OL,8,Fenforcement with the modern legal
OL,9,Ftools they need to deter, detect and
OL,10,Fdisrupt the full range of state
OL,11,Fthreats.
OL,13,F"The action counter-terrorism police
OL,14,Fhave been able to take this morning is
OL,15,Fan example that that legislation is
OL,16,Fworking well."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUxD@NO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/7
