OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1772802691
OL,3,CThree men arrested in London and Wales
OL,4,Con suspicion of spying for China
OL,6,FCommander Helen Flanagan, head of
OL,7,FCounter Terrorism Policing London,
OL,8,Fsaid: "We have seen a significant
OL,9,Fincrease in our casework relating to
OL,10,Fnational security in recent years, and
OL,11,Fwe continue to work extremely closely
OL,12,Fwith our partners to help keep the
OL,13,Fcountry safe and take action to
OL,14,Fdisrupt malign activity where we
OL,15,Fsuspect it."
OL,17,FIn addition to the addresses where the
OL,18,Fsuspects were arrested, the Met said
OL,19,Fthree other properties in London, east
OL,20,FKilbride in Scotland, and Cardiff have
OL,21,Falso been searched.
OL,26,@pD@GOUwD@LO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/7
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1772802691
OL,3,CThree men arrested in London and Wales
OL,4,Con suspicion of spying for China
OL,6,FThe force said the 39-year-old suspect
OL,7,Fwas arrested in London, the 43-year-
OL,8,Fold man was arrested in Pontyclun in
OL,9,Fsouth Wales, and the 68-year-old was
OL,10,Farrested in the county of Powys in mid-
OL,11,FWales ` with all three being detained
OL,12,Funder the Police and Criminal Evidence
OL,13,FAct.
OL,15,FMs Flanagan added: "Today's arrests
OL,16,Fare part of a proactive investigation
OL,17,Fand while these are serious matters,
OL,18,Fwe do not believe there to be any
OL,19,Fimminent or direct threat to the
OL,20,Fpublic relating to this.
OL,26,@wD@TOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/7
