OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1772802691
OL,3,CThree men arrested in London and Wales
OL,4,Con suspicion of spying for China
OL,6,F"Our investigation continues and we
OL,7,Fthank the public for their ongoing
OL,8,Fsupport."
OL,10,FA Police Scotland spokesperson said:
OL,11,F"On Wednesday March 4 2026, we carried
OL,12,Fout a search of an address in East
OL,13,FKilbride on behalf of an investigation
OL,14,Fbeing led by Counter Terrorism
OL,15,FPolicing London."
